ng","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"臺南市"}]},{"type":"text","value":": "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://tnda.tainan.gov.tw/acthouse/actcenter.asp"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"臺南市里社區活動中心列表及課程資訊"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n在活動中心的活化與多功能使用方面有許多積極的推動，以下列舉其作為優秀範例的理由："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"範例特色與推薦方向："}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多功能複合型活動中心："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 臺南市政府積極推動活動中心結合長照、小型圖書室、展演或托育等多元服務，讓空間使用率最大化，更能切中社區核心需求。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"活絡的課程與據點服務："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 許多活動中心（如臺南市的"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"謝安中民里聯合活動中心"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"鹽行里社教文化會館"}]},{"type":"text","value":"等）都有豐富的課程如歌唱、土風舞、太極拳等，並作為「關懷據點」提供服務，體現了「活化使用」的重要性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"環境改善與硬體升級："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 市府持續爭取預算進行老舊活動中心的興建、修繕與內部設備充實，提供更優質、安全的活動場所。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"溫哥華"}]},{"type":"text","value":": "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://vancouver.ca/parks-recreation-culture/creekside-community-recreation-centre.aspx"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Creekside 社區休閒中心"}]},{"type":"text","value":" (Creekside Community Recreation Centre).\n功能與設計理念： 該中心是 2010 年溫哥華冬季奧運村的一部分，其設計強調環境友善與社區功能複合。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"